{"id":1530,"category_slug":"toeic","category_name":"TOEIC Listening","position":288,"title":"Conversation 148","subtitle":"Buying a Beginner Ukulele","level":"B1","parts":15,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/toeic/conversation-148.1530/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-148-2024-09-14-18-21-32/0-conversation-148.mp3","transcript":"Excuse me. Where do you keep ukuleles?\nI'm looking for one for my music lessons.\nWhat's your price range?\nUh... About $25.\nI'm just a student, so I can't afford anything too fancy.\nPlus, I am a complete beginner.\nI'm afraid in that price range you won't be able to find any new ukuleles,\nnot even the entry-level ones.\nNow, second-hand ukuleles are often 20% or more off the original price.\nAre you open to that?\nGreat, that I can afford,\nso long as there are no serious flaws or missing strings.\nDon't worry.\nThe instruments are in excellent condition.\nLet me show you what we have in stock.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T21:02:13","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Excuse me. Where do you keep ukuleles?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-148-2024-09-14-18-21-32/1.mp3","time_start":0.68,"time_end":3.56},{"position":2,"content":"I'm looking for one for my music lessons.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-148-2024-09-14-18-21-32/2.mp3","time_start":3.56,"time_end":6.3},{"position":3,"content":"What's your price range?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-148-2024-09-14-18-21-32/3.mp3","time_start":6.5,"time_end":8.3},{"position":4,"content":"Uh... About $25.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-148-2024-09-14-18-21-32/4.mp3","time_start":8.3,"time_end":10.74},{"position":5,"content":"I'm just a student, so I can't afford anything too fancy.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-148-2024-09-14-18-21-32/5.mp3","time_start":10.74,"time_end":14.43},{"position":6,"content":"Plus, I am a complete beginner.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-148-2024-09-14-18-21-32/6.mp3","time_start":14.43,"time_end":16.68},{"position":7,"content":"I'm afraid in that price range you won't be able to find any new ukuleles,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-148-2024-09-14-18-21-32/7.mp3","time_start":16.87,"time_end":21.51},{"position":8,"content":"not even the entry-level ones.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-148-2024-09-14-18-21-32/8.mp3","time_start":21.51,"time_end":23.52},{"position":9,"content":"Now, second-hand ukuleles are often 20% or more off the original price.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-148-2024-09-14-18-21-32/9.mp3","time_start":23.52,"time_end":29.02},{"position":10,"content":"Are you open to that?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-148-2024-09-14-18-21-32/10.mp3","time_start":29.02,"time_end":30.58},{"position":11,"content":"Great, that I can afford,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-148-2024-09-14-18-21-32/11.mp3","time_start":30.58,"time_end":32.63},{"position":12,"content":"so long as there are no serious flaws or missing strings.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-148-2024-09-14-18-21-32/12.mp3","time_start":32.63,"time_end":35.97},{"position":13,"content":"Don't worry.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-148-2024-09-14-18-21-32/13.mp3","time_start":36.3,"time_end":37.2},{"position":14,"content":"The instruments are in excellent condition.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-148-2024-09-14-18-21-32/14.mp3","time_start":37.2,"time_end":39.52},{"position":15,"content":"Let me show you what we have in stock.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-1